{"tid":791914,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓咪周圍痾屎點搞","createTime":"2018-08-24T07:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:49:11.000Z","uid":6455,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"81a14ce42305de8b3a7d5a3ff07ee1a8cabe62a3","tid":791914,"uid":6455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"話說屋企有3隻貓<br />\n以前就用開礦物砂 之後發現礦物砂製造既粉塵太大<br />\n懷疑令其中一隻貓咪氣管麻麻地<br />\n之後就轉左隻木砂 點知完全唔吸味 尿壓大到不得了又好難剷走污糟左既砂 所以又決定轉砂<br />\n今次就轉左綠茶味既豆腐砂<br />\n本身對呢隻砂評價幾好 都算吸味<br />\n點知其中一隻貓咪異常奄尖<br />\n少少臭都唔肯痾 搞到喺屋企地下周圍痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經換貓砂換到幾密 但如果每痾一次都要成盆砂換真係做唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係呢隻奄尖貓係仔 其餘2隻係女<br />\n如果個貓砂盆有2隻女既味佢都唔會入去痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實已經有3個貓砂盆 等佢地一貓去一個<br />\n但係始終控制唔到邊隻貓去邊個屎坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充：3隻貓已絕育<br />\n3隻都唔算fd 各有各。但2隻女相處算好<br />\n其中一隻女一見仔行近就會fee同打隻仔<br />\n仔係最細的剛剛1歲<br />\n<br />\n又試過困籠 困住隻仔 佢喺籠入面都會痾砂盆<br />\n但係一出番黎又周圍痾<br />\n<br />\n砂又轉過 屎坑又一貓一個<br />\n隻仔已經搞到屋企人好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾地下都仲可以忍 <br />\n但有時佢會喺床痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係驚有一日佢比人掉出街<br />\n<br />\n*絕不棄養*<br />\n<br />\n希望各位連登仔可以比啲解決方法我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046c2351cda992dd638e93b187a44a9024a51d1f","tid":791914,"uid":203552,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/153856_7ed32b1d5a65f3680211f1f2cb604a0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F153856_7ed32b1d5a65f3680211f1f2cb604a0d.png&h=972907a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04e6712554909099cc91cd199477394f3baaafb9","tid":791914,"uid":42667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"貓屎好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3cb7498a7962220160a41b70dfd0eaa6d6600a","tid":791914,"uid":63490,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻貓都同你隻貓有差唔多問題<br />\n最後佢走去沖涼房個企缸屙屎屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後索性連貓砂都唔用 我老母仲話慳番一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fed6b465f17902f02c850e99e4888d2e3a4c1b5","tid":791914,"uid":67481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"試下換盤 唔係換沙<br />\n豆腐沙sofar最好用<br />\n<br />\n換個新屎坑 主人可能會喜歡"},{"pid":"c88cf369d4e53016e25fc90782849ec1347cf5aa","tid":791914,"uid":203552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fed6b465f17902f02c850e99e4888d2e3a4c1b5","tid":791914,"uid":67481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"試下換盤 唔係換沙<br />\n豆腐沙sofar最好用<br />\n<br />\n換個新屎坑 主人可能會喜歡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"我都係用豆腐砂<br />\n主人跟左我8年從來都唔會周圍屙，上星期無啦啦喺我枕頭屙左一次之後今日又黎<br />\n<br />\n我研究做錯左啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e2359183f12b8c0020d6e01c90f2d895edff62","tid":791914,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"搵籠困住佢"},{"pid":"4e5b523595523aecc26241863ce51ba62fb6a119","tid":791914,"uid":6455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"046c2351cda992dd638e93b187a44a9024a51d1f","tid":791914,"uid":203552,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2